{"tid":703804,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝本來同男朋友同埋閏蜜三個去日本玩","createTime":"2018-06-16T02:33:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T03:03:24.000Z","uid":174530,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"679bd30df543c50c73723331a9187c6aff09cd2b","tid":703804,"uid":174530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:33:02.000Z","msg":"本人真絲。<br />\n後日係小妹生日，男朋友同閏蜜早2個星期訂曬酒店機票話同我去日本慶祝。<br />\n今朝係機場準備check in果時搵唔到我本passport，明明去洗手間放低個袋比男朋友拎住果時仲係度架，攪到我搭唔到呢班機。攪左半個鐘唔知點算好，最後決定佢地2個就飛左去先，廢事浪費左張機票。<br />\n佢地話返黎同我補祝返生日，宜家呢3日突然好得閒冇野做..."},{"pid":"bc6d4fee05789ce04487ca57824ba15893c58312","tid":703804,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:35:05.000Z","msg":"假膠騙子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c08e76b12c06191777be9f188279197e9ca574","tid":703804,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:37:56.000Z","msg":"師兄世界盃睇好邊隊"},{"pid":"3641e8d587e9ded6e2f2646cf352e7adb9ca944a","tid":703804,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:43:54.000Z","msg":"去日本去得三日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c3a58ec259d571945effe347bc8707cb1c1741","tid":703804,"uid":174530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3641e8d587e9ded6e2f2646cf352e7adb9ca944a","tid":703804,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:43:54.000Z","msg":"去日本去得三日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:47:37.000Z","msg":"冇假呀ching"},{"pid":"ef5e24b6ed2ef0ae8007fcc99069e7b6fb559fc8","tid":703804,"uid":84940,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:49:20.000Z","msg":"閨你老母臭閪蜜，返去你大陸老母個臭閪度啦"},{"pid":"7cfcf744842a0aad2647acfc18f7e22566d87d2b","tid":703804,"uid":139974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:51:09.000Z","msg":"嚟我屋企幫你慶祝生日<img src=\"